-- China's Alibaba agrees to buy 50 pct stake in Guangzhou Evergrande soccer club 
-- 
-- Wed Jun 04, 2014 11:28PM EDT
-- None



BEIJING, June 5 (Reuters) - China's Alibaba Group Holding [IPO-ALIB.N] has agreed to buy a 50 percent stake in Guangzhou Evergrande Football Club, Alibaba's chairman Jack Ma and Xu Jiayin, chairman of the Evergrande group, said at a media conference on Thursday.

